    <!-- Help Topics -->
    <string name="help_topic_getting_started">Getting Started</string>
    <string name="help_content_getting_started">Welcome to FinNexus! This app helps you track your expenses, manage your budget, and analyze your spending habits.\n\nTo get started, add your first expense by tapping the + button on the home screen. You can categorize expenses, add tags, and even set recurring expenses.\n\nUse the bottom navigation to access different sections of the app: Home, History, Statistics, and Profile.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_adding_expenses">Adding Expenses</string>
    <string name="help_content_adding_expenses">To add a new expense:\n\n1. Tap the + button on the home screen\n2. Enter the amount\n3. Select a category\n4. Add optional details like vendor name, description, and tags\n5. Set the date (defaults to today)\n6. Toggle \"Recurring Expense\" if this is a regular payment\n7. Tap Save\n\nYou can edit or delete expenses later from the History screen.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_budget_management">Budget Management</string>
    <string name="help_content_budget_management">Setting a monthly budget helps you keep track of your spending limits:\n\n1. Go to the Home screen\n2. Tap \"Set Budget\"\n3. Enter your monthly budget amount\n4. Tap Save\n\nThe app will show your progress throughout the month with a visual indicator on the home screen. You\'ll also see your daily budget allowance based on the remaining days in the month.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_reports">Reports &amp; Statistics</string>
    <string name="help_content_reports">The Statistics screen provides visual insights into your spending habits:\n\n• Monthly trend shows your spending pattern over time\n• Category distribution shows where your money goes\n• Expense summary shows key metrics like highest expense and daily average\n\nYou can filter statistics by date range or by specific tags to analyze particular aspects of your spending.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_customers">Managing Customers</string>
    <string name="help_content_customers">If you\'re using the app for business expenses, you can manage customers:\n\n1. Open the navigation drawer and tap Customers\n2. View all your customers in one place\n3. Tap + to add a new customer\n4. Tap on a customer to view their details\n5. Use the options menu to edit or delete customers\n\nYou can search for specific customers using the search bar at the top.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_data_backup">Data Backup &amp; Export</string>
    <string name="help_content_data_backup">Keep your data safe by backing it up regularly:\n\n1. Go to Administration in the navigation drawer\n2. Tap \"Backup Data\" to save your data\n3. Use \"Restore Data\" to recover from a backup\n4. Export to CSV to create spreadsheet-compatible files\n\nWe recommend backing up your data before updating the app or changing devices.</string>
    
    <string name="help_topic_privacy">Privacy &amp; Security</string>
    <string name="help_content_privacy">Your financial data is important, and we take security seriously:\n\n• All data is stored locally on your device\n• Enable biometric authentication for added security\n• Backups are encrypted for your protection\n• We don\'t collect or share your expense data\n\nYou can review our full privacy policy on our website.</string>
